TEXT -416 0 Left 2 ;The bridge rectifier converts both \npositive and negative half cycles into a \nunidirectional output. The 1000 ”F capacitor\nacts as a filter, reducing ripple and\nproducing an approximately constant DC \noutput of about 10 V.
